FBIS4-35270 "drnes104_n_94005" FBIS-NES-94-104 Daily Report 28 May 1994 LEBANON Hizballah Vows Retribution for Kidnapping Hizballah Vows Retribution for Kidnapping Qasim Promises `Strongest Blow' NC2805165494 Beirut Radio Lebanon in Arabic 1530 GMT 28 May 94 NC2805165494 Beirut Radio Lebanon Arabic BFN [Text] Hizballah Deputy Secretary General Shaykh Na'im Qasim has affirmed that the confrontation arena with the enemy is wide open. He underscored the need for local peace and stability. He said: Israel has scored a point in the confrontation with the Resistance. But the men of the Resistance will continue to deal their strong blows. The strongest blow ever will be dealt to the enemy soon.
